r> <font color=#871F78>(4/4/02 2:57:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub115.ezboard.com/feqbeastlordfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/minimark.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Inner Fire</span><hr size=1> Also the best way to keep your Abjuration maxed.  Believe me people, you want Abjuration maxed when you hit 49th level.  Two very good spells come up then (Frenzy and Protect) that use it. <p><div align="center"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=120506"><img border=0  src="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/kraggan.jpg" alt="Kraggan & Bloodmaw"></a></div></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/ufrued.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Frued</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.multimania.com/foreverquest/shadowknight.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Beast Prince</span><br>  Posts: 73<br> <font color=#871F78>(4/8/02 8:10:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub115.ezboard.com/feqbeastlordfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Inner Fire</span><hr size=1> Inner Fire<br>1: Increase Armor Class (AC) from 2 (L1) to 3 (L10)<br>2: Increase Total Hit Points from 11 (L1) to 20 (L10)<br>3: Increase Current Hitpoints from 11 (L1) to 20 (L10)<br><br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>Classes: Shm (L1), Bst (L9)<br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>Skill: Abjuration<br>Allowable Targets: All<br>Beneficial: Beneficial<br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>Range to Target: 100 feet<br><br>----